ENTRY            E2814   20260116   20260227   20260227       E156
SUBENT        E2814001   20260116   20260227   20260227       E156
BIB                 10         24
TITLE      Experimental determination of the resonance width and
           the branching ratio Gamma-p1 / Gamma-p0 for the
           19.40-MeV state in 8Be for studying the 7Be(n, p1)7Li*
           reaction relevant to the cosmological lithium problem
AUTHOR     (N.Iwasa, K.Ichimura, S.Ishikawa, M.Egeta,
            T.Haginouchi, S.Ishio, S.Matsue, S.Kubono, K.Nishio,
            K.Hirose, H.Makii, R.Orlandi, F.Suzaki, J.Smallcombe)
INSTITUTE  (2JPNTOH,2JPNIPC,2JPNTOK,2JPNJAE)
REFERENCE  (J,PR/C,112,035801,2025)
PART-DET   (D,P)
SAMPLE     - Chemical-form of target is .
           - Physical-form of target is solid.
           - Target-thickness is 0.187 mg/cm2. The target was
             tilted 45 degrees, resulting in an effective
             thickness of 0.264 mg/cm2.
           - Backing is carbon.
           - Backing-thickness is 0.03 mg/cm2.
           (3-LI-7,ENR=0.994)
METHOD     (EDE)
FACILITY   (VDG,2JPNJAE) Tandem accelerator
DETECTOR   (MAGSP)
           (SCIN)
           (SISD)
HISTORY    (20251218C) Y. O.
ENDBIB              24
COMMON               1          3
EN
MEV
 28.
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           31
